text: Jos Compaan (born 2 July 1958) is a Dutch rower. She competed at the 1980 Summer Olympics, 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the Netherlands Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Purmerend
